系统的自由能 $F$ 及其微分方程为  
$$  
\begin{gathered}  
F=U-T S \\  
\mathrm{d} F=-S \,\mathrm{d} T+f \,\mathrm{d} L  
\end{gathered}  
$$  

由全微分条件得  
\begin{equation*}  
\left(\frac{\partial S}{\partial L}\right)_{T}=-\left(\frac{\partial f}{\partial T}\right)_{L}=-2 a T\left(L-L_{0}\right) \tag{2}  
\end{equation*}

设两相为 $\alpha$ 相和 $\beta$ 相，两相平衡时的 $\frac{\mathrm{d} p}{\mathrm{~d} T}$ 由克拉珀龙方程给出

$$
\frac{\mathrm{d} p}{\mathrm{~d} T}=\frac{S^{\beta}-S^{\alpha}}{V^{\beta}-V^{\alpha}}=\frac{\Delta S}{\Delta V}
$$

式中 $\Delta S$ 和 $\Delta V$ 分别表示在两相平衡时的比熵差和比容差。由此求二阶导数

$$
\begin{gathered}
\frac{\mathrm{d}^{2} p}{\mathrm{~d} T^{2}}=\frac{1}{\Delta V}\left[\Delta\left(\frac{\partial S}{\partial T}\right)_{p}+\Delta\left(\frac{\partial S}{\partial p}\right)_{T} \frac{\mathrm{~d} p}{\mathrm{~d} T}\right]-\frac{\Delta S}{(\Delta V)^{2}}\left[\Delta\left(\frac{\partial V}{\partial T}\right)_{p}+\Delta\left(\frac{\partial V}{\partial p}\right)_{T} \frac{\mathrm{~d} p}{\mathrm{~d} T}\right] \\
=\frac{\Delta c_{p}}{T \Delta V}-2 \frac{\Delta S}{(\Delta V)^{2}} \Delta\left(\frac{\partial V}{\partial T}\right)_{p}-\frac{(\Delta S)^{2}}{(\Delta V)^{3}} \Delta\left(\frac{\partial V}{\partial p}\right)_{T}
\end{gathered}
$$

其中已利用了 $\left(\frac{\partial S}{\partial T}\right)_{p}=\frac{1}{T} c_{\mathrm{p}},\left(\frac{\partial S}{\partial p}\right)_{T}=-\left(\frac{\partial V}{\partial T}\right)_{p}$ 及 $\frac{\mathrm{d} p}{\mathrm{~d} T}=\frac{\Delta S}{\Delta V}$。引入两相平衡时的相变潜热 $L^{\beta \alpha}=T \Delta S=T\left(S^{\beta}-S^{\alpha}\right)$，则上式可表示为

$$
\frac{\mathrm{d}^{2} p}{\mathrm{~d} T^{2}}=\frac{\Delta c_{\mathrm{p}}}{T \Delta V}-\frac{2 L^{\beta \alpha}}{T(\Delta V)^{2}} \Delta\left(\frac{\partial V}{\partial T}\right)_{p}-\frac{\left(L^{\beta \alpha}\right)^{2}}{T^{2} (\Delta V)^{3}} \Delta\left(\frac{\partial V}{\partial p}\right)_{T}
$$

在准静态绝热拉伸棒，从初态 $\left(T_{\mathrm{i}}, L_{\mathrm{i}}\right)$ 到终态 $\left(T_{\mathrm{f}}, L_{\mathrm{f}}\right)$，系统的熵不变，即  
$$  
S\left(T_{\mathrm{i}}, L_{\mathrm{i}}\right)=S\left(T_{\mathrm{f}}, L_{\mathrm{f}}\right)  
$$  

把式（3）中的 $S(T, L)$ 表达式代入，解得  
\begin{equation*}  
T_{\mathrm{f}}=\frac{b-a\left(L_{\mathrm{i}}-L_{0}\right)^{2}}{b-a\left(L_{\mathrm{f}}-L_{0}\right)^{2}} T_{\mathrm{i}}=\frac{\left(L_{\mathrm{i}}-L_{0}\right)^{2}-\frac{b}{a}}{\left(L_{\mathrm{f}}-L_{0}\right)^{2}-\frac{b}{a}} T_{\mathrm{i}} \tag{4}  
\end{equation*}  

由于 $a>0, b>0$ 及 $L_{f}>L_{i}>L_{0}$，所以有 $T_{\mathrm{f}}<T_{\mathrm{i}}$，即绝热拉伸棒，使棒的温度下降。

